  "events": [
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00001",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 1,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "高俊保病上。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00002",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "高俊保"
      ],
      "text": "自从那日去出阵，遇着余洪贼妖人。他用法宝将我打，翻身落马倒埃尘。因此回营得了病，昼夜坐卧不安宁。将身且把病房进，精神困倦睡沉沉。",
      "text_length": 64
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00003",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "刘金定上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00004",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "南梆子",
      "speakers": [
        "刘金定"
      ],
      "text": "后营中来了刘金定，骂一声余道洪太欺人。我这里且把病房来进，尊一声将军听分明。",
      "text_length": 38
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00005",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘金定"
      ],
      "text": "我说你醒醒！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00006",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "高俊保"
      ],
      "text": "原来是娘子来了。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00007",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘金定"
      ],
      "text": "我说你昨晚上，吃了那一服药，觉着怎么样吓？",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00008",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "高俊保"
      ],
      "text": "服药之后，近日越发沉重，只怕性命难保了！",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00009",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘金定"
      ],
      "text": "我说余洪吓余洪，我若不杀你，誓不为人也！",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00010",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "南梆子",
      "speakers": [
        "刘金定"
      ],
      "text": "我心中只把那余洪来恨，大不该害儿夫这样的苦情。奴只得画符咒将药王来请，",
      "text_length": 35
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00011",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖小开门〗，〖牌子〗。刘金定画符，仗剑烧符。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00012",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "南梆子",
      "speakers": [
        "刘金定"
      ],
      "text": "望尊神你速速降临宋营。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00013",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘金定"
      ],
      "text": "天灵灵地灵灵，药王神何在？",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00014",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "药王引小鬼同上。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00015",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮二六板",
      "speakers": [
        "药王"
      ],
      "text": "正在洞中要过瘾，忽听小鬼报一声。只因宋营刘金定，她因她丈夫得病，特地请吾师。她本是圣母高徒弟，她的法谕我是怎敢不尊？按住云头把宋营进，见了那仙姑说分明。",
      "text_length": 76
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00016",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "药王"
      ],
      "text": "吾乃药王是也。正在洞中要开灯过瘾，忽然小鬼报道，宋营刘金定有法谕相召，要叫吾神与他丈夫治病，来此已是。小鬼！",
      "text_length": 54
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00017",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "小鬼允。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00018",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "药王"
      ],
      "text": "带路一同进去。吓，仙姑请了！",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00019",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘金定"
      ],
      "text": "请了！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00020",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "药王"
      ],
      "text": "仙姑见召，有何法谕？",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00021",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘金定"
      ],
      "text": "尊神有所不知：只因我丈夫高俊保身染重病，百药不能见效，特请尊神前来替我们治上一治。",
      "text_length": 41
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00022",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "药王"
      ],
      "text": "原来如此，但不知此病是因何而起？",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00023",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘金定"
      ],
      "text": "只因番营来了一将名唤余洪，乃是一个妖道。是我丈夫在两军阵前与他交战，也不知道他用什么宝贝，将我丈夫打下马来。是奴家杀上前去，将我丈夫救回。谁知道他就病啦！也曾用药医治，总不见效。因此特请尊神到来，给我们看看，务要速速的治好了他才好。",
      "text_length": 116
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00024",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "药王"
      ],
      "text": "原来如此。仙姑但放宽心，不是小神夸口，管保是手到病除，比一把抓还要灵应些呢！",
      "text_length": 38
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00025",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘金定"
      ],
      "text": "就请尊神医治。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00026",
      "play_id": "01022008",
