      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 75,
      "seq_in_scene": 75,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘金定"
      ],
      "text": "他还说最怕吃药。一闻药味，他就呛出来了啦。还要想个法子才好。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00076",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 76,
      "seq_in_scene": 76,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "药王"
      ],
      "text": "有法子。用过山龙来吃。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00077",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 77,
      "seq_in_scene": 77,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘金定"
      ],
      "text": "什么叫做过山龙吓？",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00078",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 78,
      "seq_in_scene": 78,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "药王"
      ],
      "text": "这个过山龙，是你把这一碗药拿过来吃上一口，对着他的嘴一点一点的往里送。他自然就不能喷出来啦。",
      "text_length": 46
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00079",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 79,
      "seq_in_scene": 79,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘金定"
      ],
      "text": "我们知道啦。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00080",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 80,
      "seq_in_scene": 80,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "药王"
      ],
      "text": "这还有一个名堂。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00081",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 81,
      "seq_in_scene": 81,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘金定"
      ],
      "text": "这叫什么呀？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00082",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 82,
      "seq_in_scene": 82,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "药王"
      ],
      "text": "这叫做二仙传道。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00083",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 83,
      "seq_in_scene": 83,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘金定"
      ],
      "text": "晓得了。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00084",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 84,
      "seq_in_scene": 84,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "药王"
      ],
      "text": "吾神告过了。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00085",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 85,
      "seq_in_scene": 85,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "药王"
      ],
      "text": "这一碗灵药甚贵重，天上难找地下难寻。辞别了仙姑出宋营，吾急速回去再开灯。",
      "text_length": 36
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00086",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 86,
      "seq_in_scene": 86,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "药王"
      ],
      "text": "我回去吸我那半口鸦片烟去！",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00087",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 87,
      "seq_in_scene": 87,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "药王下，小鬼随下。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00088",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 88,
      "seq_in_scene": 88,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘金定"
      ],
      "text": "我这里将药碗拿在手，叫将军且醒来细听从头：急忙里将灵药吃一口，",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00089",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 89,
      "seq_in_scene": 89,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "刘金定对高俊保面口送药。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00090",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 90,
      "seq_in_scene": 90,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘金定"
      ],
      "text": "果然是一滴滴下了咽喉。我这里再把药吃上二口，",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00091",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 91,
      "seq_in_scene": 91,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "刘金定以口送药。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00092",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 92,
      "seq_in_scene": 92,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘金定"
      ],
      "text": "一霎时度下了十二重楼。再把那灵药吃上三口，",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00093",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 93,
      "seq_in_scene": 93,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "刘金定以口送药。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00094",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 94,
      "seq_in_scene": 94,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘金定"
      ],
      "text": "又听得他腹内鸣好似水流。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00095",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 95,
      "seq_in_scene": 95,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘金定"
      ],
      "text": "这药已经吃下去啦。但不知灵验不灵验？",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00096",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 96,
      "seq_in_scene": 96,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮导板",
      "speakers": [
        "高俊保"
      ],
      "text": "耳边厢又听得人把话讲，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00097",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 97,
      "seq_in_scene": 97,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "高俊保看。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00098",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 98,
      "seq_in_scene": 98,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "高俊保"
      ],
      "text": "一霎时只觉得遍体清凉。我身中汗津津心清气爽，",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00099",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 99,
      "seq_in_scene": 99,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "高俊保三笑。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00100",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 100,
      "seq_in_scene": 100,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "高俊保"
      ],
      "text": "再与娘子说端详。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00101",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 101,
      "seq_in_scene": 101,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "高俊保"
      ],
      "text": "吓娘子，但不知你用什么灵药医治于我，这病体竟自痊愈了！",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00102",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 102,
      "seq_in_scene": 102,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘金定"
      ],
      "text": "将军是你不知么？看看你的病症十分沉重，是奴情急无奈，特请药王老爷降下凡尘，与我开方医治，所以这个病才好的这么快。",
      "text_length": 56
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00103",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 103,
      "seq_in_scene": 103,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "高俊保"
      ],
      "text": "原来如此，多谢娘子。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00104",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 104,
      "seq_in_scene": 104,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "高俊保"
      ],
      "text": "躬身施礼把话讲，多蒙你作法请药王。若非灵药治我恙，定然一命丧无常。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00105",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 105,
      "seq_in_scene": 105,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘金定"
      ],
      "text": "将军吓！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00106",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 106,
      "seq_in_scene": 106,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘金定"
      ],
      "text": "为你病症我挂心上，夫妇恩爱也应当。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00107",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 107,
      "seq_in_scene": 107,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "高俊保"
      ],
      "text": "我今病体已愈，定要与那妖道见一高下！",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00108",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 108,
      "seq_in_scene": 108,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘金定"
      ],
      "text": "将军不必着急，歇兵三日，妾身定要灭却妖道，与将军报仇。",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00109",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 109,
      "seq_in_scene": 109,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "高俊保"
      ],
      "text": "谢娘子。请！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01022008_e00110",
      "play_id": "01022008",
      "scene_id": "01022008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 110,
      "seq_in_scene": 110,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "高俊保、刘金定同下。〖牌子〗。",
      "text_length": 15
    }
  ],
  "roles_inferred": true
}